{
  "id": "adv_event_2210_01_04",
  "title": "運命繋ぐ流星の軌跡 4話 交差した運命",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "空の色が変わってゆく",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The color of the sky changes",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "憂いも喜びも解けた色で",
      "translations": {
        "en": "to a color that combines sadness and joy",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "大人になり、どれだけ経とうとも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So that I can remain the same even",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "素顔のままいられるよう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "as time passes as I become an adult.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "運命ここで交差して",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fates crossed here",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.2,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-coast-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1266.6666667000009
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "――え？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Eh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "すみません、勝手に合わせちゃいました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry‚ I added chords to the song on my own.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "あんまり素敵な歌声だったので、つい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's such a wonderful voice that I didn't even realize it",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "お世辞はいいわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't give lip service",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "私がそんなことを言う性格だと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Did you think I was the type of person",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "思っていたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "to say things like that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "…………思わないわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "… Not really",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "貴方もお姉さん同様、そういうの嫌いでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t you hate that kind of thing too‚ like your sister?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "はい、嘘は嫌いです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ I hate lies.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "でも、莉央さんは私に一つ嘘をつきましたね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ Rio-san‚ you lied to me about one thing?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "お姉ちゃんの歌、うろ覚えだって言ってましたけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My sister's song… you said the lyrics were confusing",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "凄くうまいじゃないですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You sing really well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "バレちゃったわね。ごめんなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You heard it‚ Sorry",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "実はこの曲、好きなの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Actually‚ I like this song",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "特に、今の所の歌詞",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In particular‚ the lyrics in the previous part",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "私達の境遇に重ねてたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "overlap with our situation.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "運命交差して、って所ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is this the part where “fates crossed here”?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "私と長瀬麻奈は一瞬だけ、すれ違って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Me and Nagase Mana passed by for a moment",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "そして、もう二度と会えなくなった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and we will never meet again.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "その後、私は一年間、歌から離れた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After that‚ I stayed away from singing for a year.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、正確には離れようとしてたの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ to be exact‚ I tried to leave.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "でも、莉央さんは辞めなかった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But Rio-san didn't quit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "この歌の続き、明日を強く生きる、って言葉を",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After this song‚ as I sang the words “Live powerfully tomorrow”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "何度も口ずさむうちに、心が前を向きだしたのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "over and over again‚ my heart began to move forward.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そして、私は再びこの世界に戻る決心をした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And I decided to go back to this world",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04-rio012.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃、私はね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono‚ I…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "――はい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――yes",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "この歌を通じて、長瀬麻奈にきっと何度も",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was definitely encouraged by Mana Nagase many times",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04-rio013.m4a",
      "text": "励まされたのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "through this song.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "私が今も歌っていられるのは、間違いなく",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The reason I can still sing is because",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_04-rio014.m4a",
      "text": "彼女と、この歌に出会ったから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I met her and this song…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "一言でいい、ありがとうって伝えたい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even just one word… I want to say 'thank you'…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
